<div class = 'about'>
	
	With Jurnalo you can:<br><br>
	
	-	browse the news<br>
	-	search the news<br>
	-	subscribe to any author<br>
	-	create your own topics<br>
	-	save interesting articles to your reading list<br><br>
	
	Jurnalo ranks and sorts articles fully automatically based on relevance, quality and time. <br>
	The selection and weighting of sources is based on the sole criteria of journalistic quality. <br><br>
	
	

